HEADWORD: Sparkler
<hw>Spar"kler</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who scatters;
esp., one who scatters money; an improvident person.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

